{
  "stem": "2316.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A cave, right, with a small entrance that was covered up with leaves, and trees, and so forth, little trees, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we started to live in those.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "While it was warm we stayed outside, and we stayed in a swamp at one time because we figured while it's summer, we can survive outdoors.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there was a big, big swamp not far from us, very thick trees and close to each other.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the water was like up to here, up to your neck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we decided to go in that swamp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my dad and the other men built a bridge, a great big-- with trees.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know how they cut them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Maybe they found trees lying on the ground in the woods and they pulled them in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they built, like, a bridge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We lived on that bridge, day and night, with the snakes and the birds.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was a snake that became our pet, stayed with us all the time, never hurt us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we would-- to survive we would go out at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And mostly I, because my brother, they were afraid that he's circumcised and if they find him they'll realize that he's Jewish and force him to lead us to where we're hiding.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So was most of the time-- in the beginning, we all went for food at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We used to steal from gardens, and orchards, and-- I shouldn't have done that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
